# Security headers at the CDN/host layer — no app process exists to set these at runtime.
# Works as-is on Cloudflare Pages / Netlify; adapt syntax for CloudFront (response headers policy)
# or Azure Static Web Apps (staticwebapp.config.json) — see references/cloud-providers.md.
/*
  Content-Security-Policy: default-src 'self'; frame-ancestors 'none'
  X-Frame-Options: DENY
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Strict-Transport-Security: max-age=31536000; includeSubDomains
